#So there exist x s.t. p+x=A and q-x=A and we know that A=ceil(sqrt(N)) by the inequation showed previously

A=int(math.isqrt(N1))
A=A+1 if A*A<N1 else A
x=int(math.isqrt(A**2-N1))
#We need to find the smallest of the two integers in this case p and we find it as following
p1=A-x
